node.excerpt: Dina Magdy is working as an Automation Software Testing Engineer, starting her carreer at codescalers.
node.name: Dina Magdy
node.bio: Dina Magdy is working as an Automation Software Testing Engineer, starting her carreer at codescalers, and now has about 2 year experience in cloudcomputing software. Engineer fell in love with Threefold Threefold create future internet,so it amazing to be part of this.

node.excerpt: Dina 1 year experience in CloudComputing, getting her Bachelor degree in Communication Engineer.
node.name: Dina Abdelrahman
node.bio: Dina 1 year experience in CloudComputing, getting her Bachelor degree in Communication Engineer. Free time = Reading, Cooking, watching movies and keep in touch with technology. Engineer fell in love with Threefold I believe in ThreeFold goals and ideas. Plus, it has lots of bright minds I'm so proud to work/learn from them on a daily basis.

I strongly believe that the technology can help to create a better world and that is exactly the mission of the ThreeFold ,I find it very important for people to have equal chances, and a lot can be changed through technology these days.

The company where I learn how to own your project and manage it, like idea of new internet.

node.excerpt: A hardworking individual and a casual guy who loves to explore new ideas in Tech.
node.name: Ahmed Siddique
node.bio: A hardworking individual and a casual guy who loves to explore new ideas in Tech. Experience in Telecom/IT, Networks, Cloud and  Systems Engineering and Servers Administration. I enjoy learning new things as Learning never exhausts the mind. I have not yet come accross an organization who are rebuilding the entire ecosystem of how things work in Tech. ThreeFold is going to be huge and i want to make sure i was part of this great movement.

node.name: Ahmed Hanafy
node.bio: Ahmed is an Automation Software Testing Engineer, started his carreer at Codescalers, and now has about a year experience in Cloudcomputing software. Engineer fell in love with Threefold I believe that Threefold is changing the world by building the new neutral internet, it's a great experience to be part of this.
